    <h1>Return on Investment (ROI)</h1>
    <p class="description">A profitability metric that measures how much net gain (or loss) an investment generates relative to its cost. In marketing, it is the ultimate measure of whether a channel or campaign is worth the money.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
